{{nihongo|'''''Tokumei Kakarichō Tadano Hitoshi'''''|特命係長·只野仁||lit. "Mission Section Chief Hitoshi Tadano"|lead=yes}} is a Japanese television drama, or [[Japanese television drama|drama]] based on the popular [[manga]] of the same name by [[Kimio Yanagisawa]]. The manga is described as a "[[salaryman]] and action manga." The television drama was aired on [[TV Asahi]] in 2003, the official English name of the drama is '''Hitoshi Tadano, the Extraordinary Undercover Detective'''<ref>http://www.tv-asahihd.co.jp/e/contents/presentation/data/200702/200702_1.pdf</ref>. A new drama series started airing in 2012 as '''Detective Anonymous'''.<ref>http://www.tv-asahi.co.jp/ips/contents/Drama/</ref>

==Manga volumes==
There are two series: ''Tokumei Kakarichō Tadano Hitoshi'' (9 volumes, or [[tankōbon]], published from December 14, 2000<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ja:特命係長只野仁 (1) (ぶんか社コミックス)|publisher=Amazon.co.jp|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4821198525/ |accessdate=November 23, 2012|language=Japanese}}</ref> to June 15, 2001<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ja:特命係長只野仁 (9) (ぶんか社コミックス)|publisher=Amazon.co.jp|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4821198843/ |accessdate=November 23, 2012|language=Japanese}}</ref>) and ''Shin Tokumei Kakarichō Tadano Hitoshi'' (20 volumes, published from May 27, 2002<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ja:新・特命係長只野仁 (1) (ぶんか社コミックス)|publisher=Amazon.co.jp|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4821199521/ |accessdate=November 23, 2012|language=Japanese}}</ref> to October 25, 2007<ref>{{cite web|script-title=ja:新・特命係長只野仁 (20) (ぶんか社コミックス)|publisher=Amazon.co.jp|url=https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/4821185059/ |accessdate=November 23, 2012|language=Japanese}}</ref>). They were published by [[Kadokawa Shoten]] and [[Bunkasha]], and were serialized in ''[[Weekly Gendai]]'', a weekly manga magazine targeting salarymen.
